<plot>Tommy, a poor speller, is assigned by his teacher to write an article for the school paper, but is told that if even one word is misspelled, the article will be rejected. Later, while working on the paper, a magic voice (newsman Mike Wallace) convinces Tommy of the importance of correct spelling, and gives him five tips on how to be a better speller.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?261196</url></doc>
